    <h1>PBN (Private Blog Network)</h1>
    <p class="description">A collection of websites built by the same entity solely to create backlinks to a "money site." PBNs <strong>violate Google's Webmaster Guidelines</strong> and risk permanent removal from search results. A 20-site network costs $5,000–$15,000 to build and can be wiped out by one manual action.</p>
